name: Rajmoti Industries
overview: Established in the year 1995, we, “Rajmoti Industries”, are a trusted firm engaged in manufacturing and supplying a broad assortment of Jolly Tea Strainer, Plastic Tea Strainer, Atta Strainer, Liquid Filter and Soup & Juice Filter. Products included in this range are Colored Tea Strainer, Small Tea Strainer, Tea Strainer, Large Tea Strainer, Transparent Nylon Tea Strainer, Double Net Tea Strainer, Colored Single Net Strainer, Conical Water Strainer and others. These products are manufactured using optimum quality raw material, procured from authentic vendors of the industry, in compliance with international quality standards. Moreover, our offered range of strainers and filters is widely appreciated for its highly utility, perfect finish, durable standards, resistance against breakage, reliability and lightweight. We make the entire range available to our esteemed customers at industry leading prices in the market.
